      <title>Gensler 警告不要削弱对零售贸易商的保护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/gensler-cautions-against-weakening-guardrails-for-retail-traders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将离任的美国证券交易委员会主席加里·根斯勒（Gary Gensler）对下一届政府提出了警告：要小心不要破坏保护小型交易商的护栏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/gensler-cautions-against-weakening-guardrails-for-retail-traders</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谈判后马里将向矿工获得 12 亿美元援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/mali-to-get-1-2-billion-payment-from-miners-after-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马里对采矿业进行改革后，今年第一季度预计将从矿工那里获得 7500 亿非洲金融共同体法郎（12 亿美元）。]]></description>
